   DTSC: How to Contact Us

   How to Contact DTSC
     * Office Addresses
     * Offices Faxes
     * Phone Numbers and E-Mail Addresses of Employees
     * Phone Numbers of Major Organizational Units
     * Public Disclosure Act/File Review Requests

   At DTSC, we are committed to being honest, open, responsive, and direct
   with the public. The links below direct you to various means of giving
   us your feedback.
     * We are interested in hearing about your experiences with DTSC, both
       positive and negative. Please take a moment to complete a Cal/EPA
       Customer Survey Form, either on line or by using a printable form.
     * We want to continue to improve our web site, and your comments are
       an important part of doing that. Send your comments and suggestions
       in an e-mail to the DTSC Web Coordinator at webcoord@dtsc.ca.gov.
     * If you can't find the answer to your question on our site, our
       Public and Business Liaisons (also known as our Regional Duty
       Officers) will be able to help. You can also contact the Public and
       Business Liaison closest to you by calling (800) 72TOXIC - that's
       (800) 728-6942. From outside California, call (916) 255-3545.

   We appreciate your time and your comments.

